g.text: Agricultural facility app
USBD01 - I intend to create a dictionary of data/glossary.
USBD02 - I intend to develop the relational model (logical level).
USBD03 - I want the relational model to be instantiated (physical level).
USBD04 - I want data to be imported from a legacy system, provided in a spreadsheet.
USBD05 - I want to know the quantity of products harvested in a given portion, for each product, in a given time interval.
USBD06 - I want to know the number of protection factors applied to a given portion, for each type of factor, in a given interval of time.
USBD07 - I want to know the number of operations carried out in a given installment, for each type of operation, in a given time interval.
USBD08 - I intend to know the production factor with more applications in the agricultural installation in a given time interval.
USBD09 - I want to know the number of applications of each type of production factor applied in the agricultural installation in a given interval of time.
USBD10 - I intend to know what is the parcel with more irrigation operations in a given time interval.
USBD11 - I want to register a sowing operation.
USBD12 - I want to register a weeding operation.
USBD13 - I want to register a harvesting operation.
USBD14 - I want to register a production factor application operation.
USBD15 - I want to register a pruning operation.
USBD16 - I intend to obtain the list of factors collected from a given plot, for each species, in a given time interval.
USBD17 - I want to obtain a list of production factors applied to a given plot, and their respective quantities, for each type of component substance, in a given time interval.
USBD18 - I want to obtain the list of operations carried out on a given plot, for each type of operation, in a given time interval.

USBD19 - I intend to obtain the list of production factor applications applied in the agricultural installation, including the plot and crop (if applicable), by type of production factor, in a given time interval.
USBD20 - I want to obtain the monthly irrigation totals for each plot, in a given time interval.
USLP01 - I want to the domain model to be developed (conceptual level).
USLP02 - I want to define a functionality that consists of simulating an irrigation system controller.
USLP03 - I intend to develop a functionality that allows the irrigation plan generated by the controller simulator developed at UC22 to be automatically compressed.
USLP04 - I intend to develop functionalities that allow the evocation of UC11.
USLP05 - I intend to develop functionalities that allow the evocation of UC12.
USLP06 - I intend to develop functionalities that allow the evocation of UC13.
USLP07 - I intend to develop functionalities that allow the evocation of UC14.
USLP08 - I intend to develop functionalities that allow the evocation of UC15.
USBD21 - I want the relational model to be updated (logical and physical level) in light of new requirements and user stories.
USBD22 - I want updated data from a legacy system to be imported, provided in a spreadsheet.
USBD23 - I want the dictionary to be updated data/glossary
Agricultural Manager
Product Owner
